Lille mr Richard Seut hill
Deasterday reed. yd of the 5h & this day of 9 cur. John vale takes care for no bills
si have p £200- for acctt of S.C, & this day £200- of my acceptance with
4 dayes must pay £230- more, so shall be forced to valew on you no less the
£200- flemish, IS. did promise witheut any doubt to provide for the last E100eae e
yett kees as backward as for his other bills, & for mee to go sether i can nott, butt
if he doh not do what he promised, shall imploy mr. Sabberton to progose
artieles of sicuritie, or to sime him by lae, I doubt H.M. is deeply in with him
& happy J. if he be rot concerned with outhes att Epon or Randal att london
I hope you are not engaged with either of them, had young vander vorst here
not so good & broad a back doore of his father & boothes, he might have been
blownes up by them. god in heaven comport all loosers. HCtello mee & his
last of some thoughts he hath to make a step over to cleare all him self
which I could wish he did

remise for £62„ 15„ 9 att 21½ on m. Bandon & Garduer att 35:2 for which wher rec please

mij last to you was on the 4th curtt with a note of the contents of the 15 opheads of
cloverseed ships aboard ohn Ewings, which I supose is with you by this sime, inclosed
you gave the persect nvoyce, the charges come to more then I axspected, yett itt beeng
a furthren com. & haveing dispaled dispatched forward with 3 a 4 op headt att a time
to loose no opportunite hath cost itt sone what more then odinary what where wee
have a vessel to purpose, with in the land, to brng itt aboard of the ships that arc to
take itt in yett the goods are so much the cheaper & better, so that I am fure you
will sell as well as the best that brought any to yd markett, though by yd of 22
past you advise mee that the markett is supplysd from Rotterdam yett that can not
make the markett fall, for tis much risen heare, nay some countrey boores, will sell
by nomeanes, & dare say to kap itt & that nopt season itt must yeald 8 f whoever
to you, as you shall yudge needfull I assure you that I have don my self nt most
